      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INTUITIVE (7) goes very well this course and distance starting seven times for three wins and two minors. Below best last time at Warrnambool (22.97) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5, finishing a 10 length seventh. Appeals as a leading chance in this. ROUGH GIRL RUBY (8) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (23.80) from Box 4 at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can measure up. LAP TO BURN (5) was well fancied last time and led throughout to score (17.91) at this track in a Other over 305m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Can measure up again. FLASH GORDON (2) was well backed last start but ran below expectations when fifth (18.96), beaten 15 lengths. Some good form is emerging from his last run.",
